-- Blanchard Refining Co. Reports Emissions at Galveston Bay Plant
-- B y   M i k e   L e e
-- 2013-04-21T15:41:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-21/blanchard-refining-co-reports-emissions-at-galveston-bay-plant.html
Blanchard Refining Co. reported air
emissions at its Galveston Bay plant in Texas City, according to
a regulatory filing.  The emissions yesterday in the fluid catalystic cracking
unit lasted from 1:24 p.m. to 3:48 p.m. local time, after a
transformer rectifier tripped on an electrostatic precipitator,
according to the filing with the Texas Commission on
Environmental Quality.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Lee in Dallas at 
